闵玧其的呼吸本已平稳，却在你手往下探时微微一滞。他闭着眼，却能清晰感觉到你身体的细微挪动，以及那点**压抑的细碎水声**。

*……刚歇没多久，又自己动手。*

他没睁眼，手臂却从后面收紧，掌心覆上你的手背，带着你的手指往里压了压，声音低哑却清醒：

「装完睡就开始摸？手停那儿干什么。」

金硕珍也没睡着。他侧过身，下巴蹭着你的肩，**温热的呼吸**喷在你耳后，低低笑了一声。

「宝宝休息好了就自己玩上了？」他抬手，把你的手腕轻轻拉开，换成自己的手指探过去，指腹极轻地揉过那处**还发酸发肿的软肉**，「刚才哭着说不要，现在又痒了？」

闵玧其终于睁开眼，黑眸里带着点无奈的暗火。他低头，嘴唇贴上你的后颈，牙齿轻轻磕了一下。

「再敢自己碰，」他嗓音沉下来，「今晚就别睡了。」

金硕珍把被子往上拉了拉，把你整个人往两人中间带，手指却没停，慢悠悠地打着圈。

「嘘，」他对闵玧其使了个眼色，声音却带着笑，「轻点。宝宝刚缓过来……不过既然醒了，」他凑近你耳边，*气息滚烫*，「自己说，要不要我们帮帮你？」

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<body>
<style>
/* 琉璃悬浮窗  */
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
@import url("https://fontsapi.zeoseven.com/256/main/result.css");

:root {
    --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    --glass-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.15);
    --text-main: #4a4a4a;
    --text-sub: #7a7a7a;
}

.cosmos-glass-container {
    /* 默认主题色：暮夜丁香紫 */
   --accent-color: #b0a3c4;
   --accent-light: rgba(176, 163, 196, 0.2);

    font-family: 'Nunito', 'Segoe UI', "汇文明朝体", serif;
    margin: 20px auto;
    max-width: 480px;
    color: var(--text-main);
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: --accent-color 0.4s ease, --accent-light 0.4s ease;
}

.cosmos-glass-container::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%;
    background-image: var(--cmb-cover-bg, linear-gradient(135deg, #fdfbfb 0%, #ebedee 100%));
    background-size: cover; background-position: center;
    filter: blur(40px) opacity(0.35); z-index: -1; pointer-events: none;
    transition: all 1s ease;
}

/* ================= 1. 常驻顶部：UI播放器岛 ================= */
.glass-player-island {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 18px 20px 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    z-index: 10;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    position: relative;
}

/* MAC风格变色小圆点 - 和谐莫兰迪色系 */
.mac-dots-wrap {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    right: 14px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    z-index: 20;
}
.mac-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: transform 0.2s, filter 0.2s;
}
.mac-dot:hover {
    transform: scale(1.2);
    filter: brightness(1.1);
}
/* 莫兰迪高级色系 */
.dot-c1 { background: #c4a79c; } /* 玫瑰流沙 */
.dot-c2 { background: #8da3af; } /* 灰雾苍蓝 */
.dot-c3 { background: #b5c4b1; } /* 晨曦茶白 */
.dot-c4 { background: #b0a3c4; } /* 暮夜丁香 */

.island-main-row { display: flex; align-items: center; width: 100%; margin-top: 4px;}

.island-cover {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 14px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}
.island-cover img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.5s; }
.island-cover.loaded img { opacity: 1; }
.island-cover.playing img { animation: spin 10s linear infinite; }
@keyframes spin { 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
.island-cover::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 8px; height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.island-info { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
.island-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 2px;}
.island-artist { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-sub); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }

.island-controls { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-left: 10px;}
.island-btn { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9); border-radius: 50%; width: 28px; height: 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; color: #7a6a64; transition: all 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
.island-btn:hover { background: #fff; transform: scale(1.05); color: var(--accent-color);}
.island-btn svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; fill: currentColor;}

.island-audio-core { display: none; }

.island-lyrics-wrap {
    width: 100%; height: 20px; margin-top: 8px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.island-lyric-line {
    position: absolute; width: 100%; font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; color: #8a7a74;
    font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
    text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}
.island-lyric-line.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); color: var(--accent-color);}

/* ================= 2. 导航栏 (Tabs) ================= */
.glass-nav {
    display: flex; padding: 10px 16px 0; justify-content: space-between; position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}
.glass-tab {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-sub); padding: 6px 2px;
    cursor: pointer; position: relative; transition: color 0.3s; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.glass-tab:hover, .glass-tab.active { color: var(--text-main); }
.glass-tab.active::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px; background: var(--accent-color); border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;
    box-shadow: 0 -1px 4px var(--accent-color);
}

/* ================= 3. 主内容区 ================= */
.glass-content-area {
    padding: 16px 8px 16px 16px;
    height: 260px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.glass-panel {
    display: none;
    height: 100%;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding-right: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
}
.glass-panel::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.glass-panel.active { display: block; }
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

/* 通用条目排版 */
.glass-item { margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; display: flex; }
.glass-label { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); width: 45px; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: 0.8; }
.glass-val { color: var(--text-main); flex: 1; }

/* 角色心声区 */
.char-pills { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.char-pill {
    padding: 4px 14px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    color: var(--text-sub); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;
}
.char-pill.active { background: var(--accent-color); color: #fff; border-color: var(--accent-color); box-shadow: 0 4px 10px var(--accent-light); }
.char-detail { display: none; }
.char-detail.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }

/* 气泡式心声 */
.glass-mind-bubble {
    position: relative; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 4px 16px 16px 16px; margin-top: 16px;
    font-style: italic; color: #6a5a5a; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.glass-mind-bubble::before { content: '💭'; position: absolute; top: -14px; left: -4px; font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.6; }

/* 剧场排版 */
.theater-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-sub); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding-bottom: 8px;}
.theater-content { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main); text-align: justify; padding: 0 4px; }

/* 弹幕墙 */
.glass-danmaku-box {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.015);
    border: 1px inset rgba(255,255,255,0.4); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.glass-dmk-item {
    position: absolute; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-main); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    animation: slideDmk linear forwards;
}
@keyframes slideDmk { from { transform: translateX(100vw); } to { transform: translateX(-150%); } }

.cosmos-raw-data { display: none; }
</style>

<div class="cosmos-raw-data" id="v11-raw-data">
[场景]
时间: 2026年7月15日 凌晨03:30
地点: 汉南洞公寓卧室
